<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="KR5c0124-zh-3b06b34c" type="transl"><teiHeader><fileDesc><titleStmt><title>Liezi</title><editor role="translator">Ye Beiqing 葉蓓卿</editor></titleStmt><publicationStmt><ab>published electronically as part of the TLS project at https://hxwd.org</ab><availability status="4">The copyright status of this work is unclear</availability></publicationStmt><sourceDesc><bibl><title>Liezi</title>北京：中華書局，2011</bibl><ab>Translation of <bibl corresp="#KR5c0124"><title xml:lang="och">列子</title></bibl> into <lang xml:lang="zh">Chinese</lang>.</ab></sourceDesc></fileDesc><profileDesc><creation resp="#CH">Initially created: <date>2024-04-13T00:17:44.324+09:00</date> by CH</creation></profileDesc></teiHeader><text><body><div><head>Translated parts</head><p xml:id="KR5c0124-start"><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.40" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-13T00:19:57.413+09:00">列子说：</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.41" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-13T00:20:15.48+09:00">＂领会真意的人</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.42" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-13T00:20:56.26+09:00">什么都知道的人也无须言说。</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.43" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-13T00:21:11.444+09:00">将无言当作表述，也算是一种言说；</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.44" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-13T00:21:24.909+09:00">将无知当作知道，也算是一种有知。</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.45" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-13T00:21:42.54+09:00">而以无言作为不加表述，</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.46" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-13T00:25:33.723+09:00">以无知作为不知道，</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.47" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-13T00:25:50.644+09:00">也是一种言说和有知。</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.48" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-13T00:26:05.589+09:00">所以也没有什么不能说的，</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.49" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-13T00:26:16.195+09:00">也就没有什么不知道的；</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.52" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-13T00:26:52.077+09:00">不过如此而已。</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.50" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-13T00:26:26.4+09:00">也没有什么值得说的，</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.51" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-13T00:26:47.41+09:00">也就没有什么要知道的。</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-6a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-13T00:37:34.46+09:00">你们为什么还要无端惊惧呢？”</seg></p></div></body></text></TEI>